    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not temporary though. it feels permanent. i look at my life and i don't see anything good coming. it's just gonna be years of people whispering and me feeling like a freak. there's no point in trying to fix it when the whole world already decided who i am. it just feels like everything is stuck and there's no way out.",
